    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Variable color term referring to a range of colors in the grayish or olive range, resembling the color of greige fabric, which is raw or unfinished textile prior to bleaching or dying.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指一特定範圍的灰色或橄欖色色彩，近似於胚布的顏色。胚布指漂白或染色前的未加工布料。

</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052784/TELDAP database (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Variabele kleurenterm die verwijst naar de reeks grijsachtige of olijfkleuren die lijken op de kleur van ruw of onafgewerkt textiel dat nog niet is gebleekt of geverfd.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Termo de cor variável que se refere a uma gama de cores na faixa acinzentada ou verde-oliva, assemelhando-se à cor do tecido greige, que é um tecido cru ou inacabado antes do branqueamento ou tingimento.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
